data.description: This beautiful bi-level home is the perfect place to call home! Enjoy this gorgeous move in ready home that has been updated.  Some of the updates include recently replaced furnace, AC, and hot water tank, fully renovated full bath, updated half bath, recessed lighting in upstairs sitting room, chandelier light fixtures, and a new backyard shed. The home includes an attached garage and a large fenced in backyard with a great patio perfect for entertaining. Conveniently located with a short commute to Polaris, Easton & St. Ann's Hospital. Schedule your showing today and be one step closer to being in your new home sweet home!
